    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Well, what can I say, ladies and gentlemen? If I didn't see it with my own two eyes, I just would not believe it! Less than twenty quid for a pair of cushions fit for a king. I tell you, if His Majesty parked his arse on one of these he'd be ruined for other cushions for life. Let's get a close up - can we, Henry - so our wonderful viewers can feast their eyes on the glory of this stitching. You see that? That's as fine as you'd find on a high-end product like a Gucci bag. And this silky finish - hmmm so smooth, so sexy. I tell you, folks, if this cushion was a person, I'd happily sleep with it!" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="WELL, WHAT CAN I SAY, LADIES AND GENTLEMEN? IF I DIDN'T SEE IT WITH MY OWN TWO EYES, I JUST WOULD NOT BELIEVE IT! LESS THAN TWENTY QUID FOR A PAIR OF CUSHIONS FIT FOR A KING. I TELL YOU, IF HIS MAJESTY PARKED HIS ARSE ON ONE OF THESE HE'D BE RUINED FOR OTHER CUSHIONS FOR LIFE. LET'S GET A CLOSE UP - CAN WE, HENRY - SO OUR WONDERFUL VIEWERS CAN FEAST THEIR EYES ON THE GLORY OF THIS STITCHING. YOU SEE THAT? THAT'S AS FINE AS YOU'D FIND ON A HIGH-END PRODUCT LIKE A GUCCI BAG. AND THIS SILKY FINISH - HMMM SO SMOOTH, SO SEXY. I TELL YOU, FOLKS, IF THIS CUSHION WAS A PERSON, I'D HAPPILY SLEEP WITH IT!" Visible="No"/>
