    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Before we get started, I have some sad news.  You've probably noticed John Wickerby isn't with us today and he won't be with us tomorrow or in fact ever again. In the early hours of this morning, he shot himself in the head with a nail gun.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="BEFORE WE GET STARTED, I HAVE SOME SAD NEWS.  YOU'VE PROBABLY NOTICED JOHN WICKERBY ISN'T WITH US TODAY AND HE WON'T BE WITH US TOMORROW OR IN FACT EVER AGAIN. IN THE EARLY HOURS OF THIS MORNING, HE SHOT HIMSELF IN THE HEAD WITH A NAIL GUN.'" Visible="No"/>
