    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="LOOK AT YOU! A MAN YOU'VE WORKED WITH FOR OVER A DECADE HAS DIED. HIS WIFE IS DEAD AND SO ARE HIS TWO CHILDREN AND YOU'RE FUCKING REJOICING.'" Visible="No"/>
