    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="If you can get those poster designs over to me this evening, that would be great. Otherwise tomorrow morning will do. In the meantime, I'm emailing you a couple of designs I want you to keep under your hat for now.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="IF YOU CAN GET THOSE POSTER DESIGNS OVER TO ME THIS EVENING, THAT WOULD BE GREAT. OTHERWISE TOMORROW MORNING WILL DO. IN THE MEANTIME, I'M EMAILING YOU A COUPLE OF DESIGNS I WANT YOU TO KEEP UNDER YOUR HAT FOR NOW.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="For Butcher Baby's friends. If Butcher Baby sells as well as you and I both know it will, then we're planning on creating a range of dolls. Barbie has Ken. Sindy has Paul. And Butcher Baby will have Psycho Sam and Man-Hater Mandy. What do you think?'" Visible="No"/>
