    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Yes, I think so. By the way, Tom, I've divided to reinstate Karl. He may be a dick but he is the greatest sales manager in the country. If we're to make Butcher Baby a success, we really need him aboard. I hope you understand.'" Visible="No"/>
