    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="These pictures appear to show a Saturn V rocket about to be launched from Cape Canaveral.' The man from the BBC shuffled some papers on his desk. Then he pressed a finger against his earpiece and nodded thoughtful as someone spoke to him. After a couple of nods and a hmm-hmm, he left the earpiece alone and spoke to the camera. 'The White House have just confirmed that at approximately 9PM Eastern Daylight Time - that's 1AM GMT - NASA launched a Saturn V from Cape Canaveral but have decline to give any reason for doing so." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="THESE PICTURES APPEAR TO SHOW A SATURN V ROCKET ABOUT TO BE LAUNCHED FROM CAPE CANAVERAL.' THE MAN FROM THE BBC SHUFFLED SOME PAPERS ON HIS DESK. THEN HE PRESSED A FINGER AGAINST HIS EARPIECE AND NODDED THOUGHTFUL AS SOMEONE SPOKE TO HIM. AFTER A COUPLE OF NODS AND A HMM-HMM, HE LEFT THE EARPIECE ALONE AND SPOKE TO THE CAMERA. 'THE WHITE HOUSE HAVE JUST CONFIRMED THAT AT APPROXIMATELY 9PM EASTERN DAYLIGHT TIME - THAT'S 1AM GMT - NASA LAUNCHED A SATURN V FROM CAPE CANAVERAL BUT HAVE DECLINE TO GIVE ANY REASON FOR DOING SO." Visible="No"/>
