    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Yes, it is hard to make sense of. Clearly, this all has something to do with the Black Knight satellite.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="YES, IT IS HARD TO MAKE SENSE OF. CLEARLY, THIS ALL HAS SOMETHING TO DO WITH THE BLACK KNIGHT SATELLITE.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Is it possible that its payload is some sort of top secret weapon which they believe can put paid to the Black Knight?'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="IS IT POSSIBLE THAT ITS PAYLOAD IS SOME SORT OF TOP SECRET WEAPON WHICH THEY BELIEVE CAN PUT PAID TO THE BLACK KNIGHT?'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Da, it's possible but who can say? And even if it is a weapon, there is no guarantee that it will be effective. Remember, we have thrown several gigatons of atomic warheads at this beast and what good has it done? We might as well be using bows and arrows.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="DA, IT'S POSSIBLE BUT WHO CAN SAY? AND EVEN IF IT IS A WEAPON, THERE IS NO GUARANTEE THAT IT WILL BE EFFECTIVE. REMEMBER, WE HAVE THROWN SEVERAL GIGATONS OF ATOMIC WARHEADS AT THIS BEAST AND WHAT GOOD HAS IT DONE? WE MIGHT AS WELL BE USING BOWS AND ARROWS.'" Visible="No"/>
