    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="We're joining our reporter, Phoebe Anderson who has tracked down the conspiracy theorist Layton Jackson, leader of the League Against Disinformation. As you may have seen earlier, the League held a demonstration on Westminster Green in an attempt to prove that the Black Knight is a hoax. Many of those demonstrators are now dead, having been attacked and half-eaten by their companions." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="WE'RE JOINING OUR REPORTER, PHOEBE ANDERSON WHO HAS TRACKED DOWN THE CONSPIRACY THEORIST LAYTON JACKSON, LEADER OF THE LEAGUE AGAINST DISINFORMATION. AS YOU MAY HAVE SEEN EARLIER, THE LEAGUE HELD A DEMONSTRATION ON WESTMINSTER GREEN IN AN ATTEMPT TO PROVE THAT THE BLACK KNIGHT IS A HOAX. MANY OF THOSE DEMONSTRATORS ARE NOW DEAD, HAVING BEEN ATTACKED AND HALF-EATEN BY THEIR COMPANIONS." Visible="No"/>
