    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Yes it is, Stanley. I've managed to catch up with Mr Jackson here in a very deserted Hyde Park. If you listen, you'll hear something that's not been heard in at this time of day in central London for hundreds of years - namely silence. There is no traffic - at least none that's moving - and there are no people. Here, at least, the curfew is working." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="YES IT IS, STANLEY. I'VE MANAGED TO CATCH UP WITH MR JACKSON HERE IN A VERY DESERTED HYDE PARK. IF YOU LISTEN, YOU'LL HEAR SOMETHING THAT'S NOT BEEN HEARD IN AT THIS TIME OF DAY IN CENTRAL LONDON FOR HUNDREDS OF YEARS - NAMELY SILENCE. THERE IS NO TRAFFIC - AT LEAST NONE THAT'S MOVING - AND THERE ARE NO PEOPLE. HERE, AT LEAST, THE CURFEW IS WORKING." Visible="No"/>
