    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'TOM CAXTON.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'MR. CAXTON, YOU PROBABLY DON'T KNOW ME. I'M ISABELLE LINTON.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'OH YES. KARL'S WIFE.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;ALL THE FEAR AND TREPIDATION OF THE PAST FEW DAYS CAME FLOODING OUT OF TOM. HE LAUGHED UNTIL HE WAS TOO WEAK TO LAUGH ANY MORE." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'I'M CALLING FROM THE HOSPITAL,' SAID ISABELLE LINTON, HER VOICE FAINT, HER BREATHING HEAVY. 'THERE'S NO CHANCE OF RESCUING KARL'S PENIS. THEY CAN GREW HIM A NEW ONE IN A LABORATORY BUT THERE'S BEEN SUCH A SPATE OF MEN LOSING THEIR DICKS HE'S GOING TO HAVE TO WAIT AT LEAST THREE YEARS, BY WHICH TIME I'LL BE A HAPPY DIVORCEE.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'WELL, GOOD LUCK TO YOU, MRS LINTON. JUST ONE THING THOUGH. I'M CURIOUS AS TO WHY YOU RANG ME TO TELL ME THIS?'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'I'M RINGING EVERYONE ON KARL'S PHONE. SOMETHING LIKE THIS IS TOO GOOD TO KEEP TO ONE'S SELF. NOW, IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME, I HAVE QUITE A FEW MORE CALLS TO MAKE. GOODBYE, MR. CAXTON. LOOK OUT FOR YOUR PENIS NOW.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;AND WITH THAT, THE SOON-TO-BE-DIVORCED ISABELLE LINTON HUNG UP LEAVING TOM TO WONDER WHAT THE FUCK WAS WRONG WITH HIS HEAD." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;IT WAS ALL TOO MUCH." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;THE MAN HAD NO DICK!" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;NOW -" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;AND NOW -" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;POOR OLD KARL LINTON! HE'D ALWAYS BEEN SO PROUD OF HIS PENIS. HAD BOASTED OF ITS SIZE. HAD, ONE DRUNKEN NIGHT DOWN THE PUB, TAKEN IT OUT AND SLAPPED IT ON A TABLE FOR ALL TO SEE AND WORSHIP." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;HEARING HIS LAUGHTER, ISABELLE LINTON LAUGHED ALL THE MORE, WHICH POURED PETROL ON THE FLAMES OF TOM CAXTON'S MIRTH." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;THEN HE PICTURED AN EMASCULATED KARL LINTON WATCHING CHERI MAHLER CHEW HIS DICK LIKE IT WAS PASTRAMI AND LOST IT. HE HOWLED AND HE WHOOPED. HE CONVULSED AND DOUBLED OVER. TEARS FILLED HIS EYES, MADE TRACKS DOWN HIS CHEEKS. HIS LUNGS STRUGGLED TO KEEP UP. HIS DIAPHRAGM WENT CRAZY, CAUSING HIM TO HICCUP." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;THEN HIS SMILE BROADENED INTO A GRIN." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;BUT HER LAUGHTER WAS INFECTIOUS AND TOM FOUND HIMSELF SMILING." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;HE WONDERED IF THE WOMAN WASN'T INSANE. THERE WAS CERTAINLY A HYSTERICAL EDGE TO HER CACKLING THAT SUGGESTED SHE HAD COMPLETELY LOST THE PLOT." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;TOM WAS APPALLED." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;ISABELLE LINTON CRACKED UP. HER LAUGHTER CAME AT HIM IN STACCATO BURSTS THAT SOUNDED MORE ANIMAL THAN HUMAN." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'ANYWAY, JUST AFTER THE BLACK KNIGHT HAD BEEN AND GONE, I GOT A PHONE CALL. WHEN I SAW WHO IT WAS FROM, I NEARLY DIDN'T ANSWER BUT I'M GLAD I DID. AND WHEN I SAY GLAD, I MEAN ECSTATIC. THERE'S NO SWEETER SOUND THAN HEARING YOUR PHILANDERING HUSBAND SCREAMING LIKE A LITTLE GIRL." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'AND YOU KNOW WHAT HE WAS SCREAMING? HOLD ON TO YOUR SIDES BECAUSE THIS IS GOING TO GET YOU LAUGHING TILL YOU PUKE. MY PENIS! HE SCREAMED. THE BITCH HAS EATEN MY PENIS!'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'LAST NIGHT, WHEN HE SHOULD HAVE BEEN HOME PROTECTING HIS LOVING WIFE AND CHILDREN, WHERE DO YOU THINK THE RANDY BASTARD WAS? YEAH - CHERI'S, THAT'S WHERE. DIDN'T EVEN BOTHER LYING ABOUT IT." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'IT'S ABOUT MY HUSBAND. I TAKE IT YOU KNOW HE HAD A MISTRESS. IT'S THE SORT OF THING HE LIKES TO BOAST ABOUT. HER NAME'S CHERI, IN CASE YOU WERE WONDERING. OR DID HE TELL YOU THAT?" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'I CAN'T IMAGINE THERE'S ANYTHING CAN MAKE ME LAUGH RIGHT NOW, BUT YOU'RE WELCOME TO TRY.'" Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="&#xA;'WOULD YOU LIKE A GOOD LAUGH, MR. CAXTON?'" Visible="No"/>
