    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="You've got something on your chin.' Tom took out his handkerchief and spat on it. He dabbed at his wife's chin until all the blood was gone. 'There now. That's better. We'll soon have you looking your old self again." Visible="No"/>
