    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="patronising and supercilious, these are without doubt the darkest days our nation has ever faced. We are in the midst of an emergency so dire I was left with no choice but to declare martial law - to effectively turn these hallowed isles, this bastion of democracy, into a police state." Visible="No"/>
    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="PATRONISING AND SUPERCILIOUS, THESE ARE WITHOUT DOUBT THE DARKEST DAYS OUR NATION HAS EVER FACED. WE ARE IN THE MIDST OF AN EMERGENCY SO DIRE I WAS LEFT WITH NO CHOICE BUT TO DECLARE MARTIAL LAW - TO EFFECTIVELY TURN THESE HALLOWED ISLES, THIS BASTION OF DEMOCRACY, INTO A POLICE STATE." Visible="No"/>
