    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="Until this moment, Neil Armstrong was undoubtedly the world's most famous astronaut,' said the BBC man, speaking invisibly over a shot of the earth seen through a window, 'but surely from here on in, the names of these two brave men Jurgen Fischer and Walter Penrose will eclipse even that of the first man on the moon.'" Visible="No"/>
