    <Character Color="#FFFFFFFFFFFF" Name="I have a visual sighting of the Black Knight satellite. It's hard to make out because it really is black. I would say that's the blackest thing I've ever seen. About the only thing I can say about it is that it's quiet irregular in shape.'" Visible="No"/>
